    <item>
      <title>越南议会批准670亿美元高铁项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/vietnam-parliament-approves-67-billion-high-speed-rail-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南政府计划实施大型基础设施项目来支持其经济增长目标，将于 2027 年开始建设投资 670 亿美元的高铁网络，连接其北部和南部省份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/vietnam-parliament-approves-67-billion-high-speed-rail-project</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 08:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迅销集团关注新疆言论后中国抵制行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/fast-retailing-watching-for-china-boycott-after-xinjiang-remarks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[优衣库 (Uniqlo) 服装连锁店的母公司迅销 (Fast Retailing Co.) 正在密切关注中国对其产品的需求是否受到董事长柳井正 (Tadashi Yanai) 据称未使用新疆棉花的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/fast-retailing-watching-for-china-boycott-after-xinjiang-remarks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 08:06:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格鲁吉亚总理称在冲突中不会看到基辅式的“独立广场”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/georgian-police-begin-clearing-streets-after-protesters-regroup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚总理将首都抗议者与警方第二晚发生的暴力冲突归咎于“激进分子及其外国首领”，此次冲突的起因是执政党表示将把与欧盟就潜在成员国身份的谈判推迟数年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/georgian-police-begin-clearing-streets-after-protesters-regroup</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 03:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
